const longDescription =
  "Beyond the major trades, we handle the dozens of small jobs homeowners need but most contractors decline: <strong>appliance installation, drywall patching, fixture installs, pre-listing inspections, insurance paperwork, smart-home setup, and one-off projects</strong>. Hourly handyman rate is $145/hour with a 1-hour minimum and no hidden trip charge. If your small job uncovers a real HVAC, plumbing, or electrical issue, we have the right licensed technician on staff — no second contractor required.";
